.TH vdf_get_int_recursive 3

.SH NAME
vdf_get_int_recursive

.SH LIBRARY
Valve Data Format Parser Library (libvdfc)

.SH SYNOPSIS
#include <vdfc/vdf.h>

int vdf_get_int_recursive(const VDFNode *object, const char *key, int fallback);

.SH DESCRIPTION
Look up `key` anywhere in the subtree rooted at `object`, depth-first, and return its integer value.

If no matching integer node is found anywhere in the subtree, returns `fallback`.

.SH RETURN VALUE
Returns the matching node's integer value, or `fallback`.

.SH ERRORS
None.

